import React from 'react';
import { Header, Button, Icon, Segment, Grid, Divider, Image, Responsive, SegmentGroup, Container } from 'semantic-ui-react'


const Home = () => {

    return (
        <Container>
            <Segment color='violet' padded='very'>
                <Segment.Group horizontal raised>
                    <Segment raised color='teal' hover=''><Icon name='facebook' size='huge' /></Segment>
                    <Segment color='teal'><Icon name='github' size='huge' /></Segment>
                    <Segment color='teal'><Icon name='linkedin' size='huge' /></Segment>
                    <Segment color='teal'><Icon name='mail' size='huge' /></Segment>
                </Segment.Group>
                <Grid divided>
                    <Grid columns={3} relaxed='very' stackable>
                        <Grid.Column>
                            1st column
                        </Grid.Column>
                        <Grid.Column>
                            2nd column
                        </Grid.Column>
                        <Grid.Column>
                            3rd column
                        </Grid.Column>
                    </Grid>
                </Grid>
            </Segment>
        </Container >
    )
};

export default Home;
